Benchmark programs for the MPI library on SMP clusters.

Micro-benchmarks:
allreduce.c  	: MPI_Allreduce
bar_test.c   	: MPI_Barrier
bcast_test1.c  	: same root MPI_Bcast
bcast_test2.c  	: rotating root MPI_Bcast
bcast_test3.c  	: combo root MPI_Bcast
cpuid.c        	: MPI_Get_processor_name
gene_test.c  	: the initial test
ow_dat.c     	: one-way data send/receive
pp.c      		: ping-pong test with 512 bytes data
pp_dat.c  		: ping-pong test with variable sized data
reduce_test1.c 	: same root MPI_Reduce
reduce_test2.c 	: rotating root MPI_Reduce
reduce_test3.c	: combo root MPI_Reduce
srtest.c		: ping-pong with random sleep

ex.mpich/		: experiments from MPICH
